OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1775210759
OL,3,CBreast cancer patients call for 'no
OL,4,Cstone left unturned' in failings probe
OL,6,FBreast cancer patients are calling for
OL,7,F"no stone to be left unturned" as
OL,8,Finvestigations continue into failings
OL,9,Fin treatments and care at County
OL,10,FDurham and Darlington NHS Foundation
OL,11,FTrust.
OL,13,FA review of past cases was launched
OL,14,Fafter a catalogue of issues was
OL,15,Frevealed, ranging from delayed
OL,16,Fdiagnoses to unnecessary surgery and
OL,17,Foutdated clinical practices.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/21
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1775210759
OL,3,CBreast cancer patients call for 'no
OL,4,Cstone left unturned' in failings probe
OL,6,FSo far, the review has identified that
OL,7,Fmore than 50 patients came to moderate
OL,8,For severe harm. Patients say that as
OL,9,Fthat process continues, thoroughness
OL,10,Fis key.
OL,12,FYvonne Staley, 85, has received an
OL,13,Fapology from the trust over her
OL,14,Ftreatment which began in 2021.
OL,16,F"I was furious," she said. "I felt
OL,17,Fanger inside that people that I'd
OL,18,Ftrusted, because they know their job,
OL,19,Fhad let me down at my most vulnerable
OL,20,Ftime."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/21
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1775210759
OL,3,CBreast cancer patients call for 'no
OL,4,Cstone left unturned' in failings probe
OL,6,FMrs Staley describes the atmosphere
OL,7,Fshe experienced as a "conveyor belt"
OL,8,Fwhich was highly impersonal.
OL,10,FAt the time, she says she accepted it
OL,11,Fsimply as the modern way, combined
OL,12,Fwith the impact of Covid.
OL,14,FThen, at the end of 2025, the trust
OL,15,Ftold her it had identified a number of
OL,16,Fissues with her treatment, including
OL,17,Fthe fact that one of her surgeries
OL,18,Fmight have been prevented, had she
OL,19,Freceived a more timely diagnosis.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/21
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1775210759
OL,3,CBreast cancer patients call for 'no
OL,4,Cstone left unturned' in failings probe
OL,6,FMrs Staley said the news came as a
OL,7,Fhuge shock.
OL,9,FIndependent reports, published in
OL,10,F2025, identified a series of failings
OL,11,Fwith breast surgery services within
OL,12,FCounty Durham and Darlington NHS
OL,13,FFoundation Trust dating back to 2012.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/21
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1775210759
OL,3,CBreast cancer patients call for 'no
OL,4,Cstone left unturned' in failings probe
OL,6,FThe Aubrey Report, which was released
OL,7,Fin November 2025, concluded that some
OL,8,Fpatients had come to avoidable harm
OL,9,Fthrough delayed diagnoses and
OL,10,Funnecessary surgeries, leading to
OL,11,Fphysical, emotional and psychological
OL,12,Fimpacts on staff as well as the
OL,13,Fpatients themselves.
OL,15,FIt highlighted examples of poor
OL,16,Fclinical practice which was allowed to
OL,17,Fcontinue because of failures in
OL,18,Fgovernance and leadership.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/21
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1775210759
OL,3,CBreast cancer patients call for 'no
OL,4,Cstone left unturned' in failings probe
OL,6,FAs part of its response, the trust
OL,7,Fembarked on what it calls a 'look-back
OL,8,Freview' of past cases to identify
OL,9,Fpatients who may have been harmed.
OL,11,FIt is currently focusing largely on
OL,12,Fthe period from 2023 to February 2025,
OL,13,Fwhere:
OL,15,FThe trust has stressed that the
OL,16,Fcurrent review timeframe will be
OL,17,Fextended to include earlier years -
OL,18,Fsomething Mrs Staley believes is
OL,19,Fessential to fully understand its
OL,20,Fimpacts.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/21
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1775210759
OL,3,CBreast cancer patients call for 'no
OL,4,Cstone left unturned' in failings probe
OL,6,F"How did it grow into this monster?"
OL,7,Fshe asked, adding, "And it was a
OL,8,Fmonster because people have been
OL,9,Fdamaged in all different ways."
OL,11,FThe call for a full examination of
OL,12,Fpast cases is echoed by another breast
OL,13,Fcancer patient, who we are calling
OL,14,FElla.
OL,16,FShe has asked us to protect her
OL,17,Fidentity as a result of the distress
OL,18,Fshe has faced over her breast cancer
OL,19,Fdiagnosis, treatment and its aftermath.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/21
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1775210759
OL,3,CBreast cancer patients call for 'no
OL,4,Cstone left unturned' in failings probe
OL,6,FElla believes that after an operation
OL,7,Fin 2019 to remove pre-cancerous
OL,8,Fgrowths, her continuing concerns were
OL,9,Fnot taken seriously.
OL,11,FIn 2022 she was diagnosed with breast
OL,12,Fcancer.JElla also says a failure, at
OL,13,Fthe time, to offer her reconstructive
OL,14,Fsurgery has had a devastating impact.
OL,16,F"Cancer's changed me completely," she
OL,17,Fsaid. "It's when I shower, when I
OL,18,Fbathe, it's just ugly, if you like and
OL,19,FI don't feel full any more, I'm not
OL,20,Fthat person any more."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/21
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1775210759
OL,3,CBreast cancer patients call for 'no
OL,4,Cstone left unturned' in failings probe
OL,6,FElla is waiting to hear if her case
OL,7,Fwill be reviewed. For her, full
OL,8,Fexamination of patient cases is
OL,9,Fessential to fully understand how and
OL,10,Fwhy failures occurred.
OL,12,F"When something goes wrong in cancer
OL,13,Fcare, the consequences are life
OL,14,Fchanging but not just for me, it's for
OL,15,Fother women," she explained.
OL,17,F"There just needs to be no stone
OL,18,Funturned and it's the trust we need
OL,19,Fthat accountability from."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/21
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1775210759
OL,3,CBreast cancer patients call for 'no
OL,4,Cstone left unturned' in failings probe
OL,6,FCounty Durham and Darlington NHS
OL,7,FFoundation Trust is clear that its
OL,8,Flook-back review of cases will be
OL,9,Fextended, prior to 2023.
OL,11,FThe question is how far back it will
OL,12,Fstretch.
OL,14,FThe organisation's chief nurse, Gill
OL,15,FHunt, says the organisation is working
OL,16,Fwith patients, independent clinicians
OL,17,Fand taking legal soundings to agree
OL,18,Fits scope.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G10/21
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1775210759
OL,3,CBreast cancer patients call for 'no
OL,4,Cstone left unturned' in failings probe
OL,6,FShe says the trust recognises the
OL,7,Fdecision will have "significant
OL,8,Fimplications" for patients, which is
OL,9,Fwhy it is important to agree a date
OL,10,Fthat is "the right one for people".
OL,12,FAs the look-back review continues,
OL,13,FCounty Durham and Darlington NHS
OL,14,FFoundation Trust is also facing
OL,15,Fquestions over the future of Amir
OL,16,FBhatti who was its clinical lead for
OL,17,Fbreast services.
OL,19,FThe trust has confirmed that while Mr
OL,20,FBhatti is still employed, he is not
OL,21,Fworking with patients.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G11/21
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1775210759
OL,3,CBreast cancer patients call for 'no
OL,4,Cstone left unturned' in failings probe
OL,6,FIn a statement from its acting medical
OL,7,Fdirector, Dr Shafie Kammaruddin
OL,8,Fexplained: "Mr Bhatti is currently
OL,9,Frestricted from any clinical duties.
OL,10,FThis means that he is not seeing
OL,11,Fpatients or providing any clinical
OL,12,Fcare or treatment.
OL,14,F"We recognise the concerns being
OL,15,Fraised and understand the importance
OL,16,Fof transparency. We are taking the
OL,17,Fconcerns seriously and are following
OL,18,Fthe appropriate processes.
OL,26,@pD@LOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G12/21
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1775210759
OL,3,CBreast cancer patients call for 'no
OL,4,Cstone left unturned' in failings probe
OL,6,F"As part of the trust's ongoing review
OL,7,Finto the breast surgery service, there
OL,8,Fis an active investigation underway.
OL,9,FWhile this process is ongoing, we are
OL,10,Fnot able to share further detail."
OL,12,FMr Bhatti was approached for comment
OL,13,Fand provided the following statement:
OL,14,F"I am grateful for the opportunity to
OL,15,Frespond but I am cooperating fully
OL,16,Fwith the trust investigations, and it
OL,17,Fwould be inappropriate for me to
OL,18,Fcomment further whilst proceedings are
OL,19,Fongoing."
OL,26,@vD@AOU{D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G13/21
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
