PN,42214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1775210759
OL,3,CBreast cancer patients call for 'no
OL,4,Cstone left unturned' in failings probe
OL,6,FCounty Durham and Darlington NHS
OL,7,FFoundation Trust has also said it is
OL,8,Fsupporting Durham Police which has
OL,9,Flaunched its owns appeal in relation
OL,10,Fto the breast cancer services
OL,11,Finvestigations.
OL,13,FThe force is inviting people to come
OL,14,Fforward with information relating to
OL,15,Fthe period between 1 January 2023 and
OL,16,F21 February 2025.
OL,18,FA dedicated portal has been created on
OL,19,Fit website for people to report
OL,20,Fdetails.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G14/21
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42215
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1775210759
OL,3,CBreast cancer patients call for 'no
OL,4,Cstone left unturned' in failings probe
OL,6,FA spokesman for Durham Constabulary
OL,7,Fsaid: "Durham Constabulary received an
OL,8,Fallegation relating to breast cancer
OL,9,Fservices at the County Durham and
OL,10,FDarlington NHS Foundation Trust.
OL,12,F"Following consultation with the Crown
OL,13,FProsecution Service, officers are
OL,14,Finvestigating that allegation to
OL,15,Festablish the facts and review
OL,16,Fmaterial to determine if any criminal
OL,17,Foffences have occurred.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G15/21
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42216
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1775210759
OL,3,CBreast cancer patients call for 'no
OL,4,Cstone left unturned' in failings probe
OL,6,F"We would stress that the
OL,7,Finvestigation remains in its early
OL,8,Fstages and detectives from the Major
OL,9,FCrime Team are liaising with the
OL,10,Ftrust, which is supporting the
OL,11,Finquiry."
OL,13,FAmid the continuing discussions as to
OL,14,Fthe scope of the trust's look-back
OL,15,Freview, a legal representative for
OL,16,Fsome breast cancer patients is calling
OL,17,Ffor maximum transparency.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G16/21
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42217
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1775210759
OL,3,CBreast cancer patients call for 'no
OL,4,Cstone left unturned' in failings probe
OL,6,FFrancesca Paul, a partner at Fletchers
OL,7,FSolicitors said: "It is vital that all
OL,8,Fpossible cases are identified, and
OL,9,Fthat patients receive clear answers
OL,10,Fabout their care."
OL,12,FMs Paul added: "Limiting the timeframe
OL,13,Frisks missing earlier failings and
OL,14,Fdenying some women theJopportunity for
OL,15,Freview, support, or appropriate follow-
OL,16,Fup."
OL,18,FMeanwhile, Mrs Staley is among a
OL,19,Fnumber of women being supported by the
OL,20,Flegal firm Slater and Gordon.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G17/21
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
