OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42219
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1775210759
OL,3,CBreast cancer patients call for 'no
OL,4,Cstone left unturned' in failings probe
OL,6,FAlongside its look-back process,
OL,7,FCounty Durham and Darlington NHS
OL,8,FFoundation Trust has help and
OL,9,Fpsychological support in place for
OL,10,Fwomen who have been affected by its
OL,11,Ffailings in breast surgery services.
OL,13,FIt is also in the early stages of
OL,14,Festablishing a patient support group
OL,15,Ffor women to share their experiences.
OL,17,FIn addition, chief nurse, Gill Hunt,
OL,18,Fsays for patients requiring breast
OL,19,Fcancer services now, treatment and
OL,20,Fcare are very different.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G19/21
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42220
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1775210759
OL,3,CBreast cancer patients call for 'no
OL,4,Cstone left unturned' in failings probe
OL,6,FShe said: "We've recruited external
OL,7,Fexperts, we have a multi-professional
OL,8,Fapproach, we have improved access to
OL,9,Fdiagnostics and our current outcomes
OL,10,Fare in line with or better than the
OL,11,Fnational average."
OL,13,FAfter traumatic times, the trust has
OL,14,Fembarked on rebuilding confidence in
OL,15,Fbreast surgery services, not only with
OL,16,Fcommunities but also with its staff.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G20/21
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
